title: All Documents On File (United States Secret Service)

communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the Freedom of Information Act, I hereby request the following records: Any and all current records pertaining to Mason C. Turner DOB June 2, 1997 FBI Ref No.: WN82XELN8

Sincerely,

Mason C. Turner
